Class HashMapMulti<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elkoserver.util.HashMapMulti<K,V>

  • public class HashMapMulti<K,V>
extends Object
    A hashtable-like collection that maps each key to a set of items rather than to a single item.
